trans:
Nor - I never get sulky at P'.
LorLorKor - Really? You might not know but Ling doesn't tell you. Nong Orm is cute.
Nor - P'Ling is not usually sulky but P'Ling easily gets high blood pressure.
(Fanclub shouts that P'Ling is more sulky.)
LorLorKor - Why? When was Ling sulky?
Nor - I will send the clip to you to see. Maybe you won't go to see TikTok.
Who likes to say missing more? (Both point at Nong Orm.)
Nor - I see him every day. When I don't see him, I will miss him. Yesterday, when we filmed a show together, the first word Orm said was Lingling, and Quong missed you.
LorLorKor - Nong Orm always says, I love u Lingling.
Host - How do you feel when you hear it?
LorLorKor - Cute.
Fanclub - Cute, then do you love?
(Then, Ling Orm is whispering something to each other.)
Who likes to come to hug more? (Both point at Nong Orm.)
Nor - We are stuck with skinship.
Nor - But we are like this with just a person we are close with. The one we feel relaxed to be with.
LorLorKor - Ling is a person who is not often skinship.
Fanclub - Do you want to try? Let's try.
Nor - In both their eyes, not aware of anything. ~ üé∂
LorLorKor - Do you understand introvert?
Who is crazier about love? (Points to yourself)
